{"id":6240,"author":"~Xenon~","author_avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D","author_id":682,"author_status":1,"gmt_create":1638539913964,"gmt_modified":1638539913964,"content":"来讲一讲我上过的通识/跨学院选修课吧！\n田径（体育类）\n内容包括了长跑、短跑、跨栏、跳高、跳远和铅球这六个项目，老师是裁判员出身，所以课上除了训练动作技术以外，也会讲解田径比赛中的细致规则和争议裁判。考核较为丰富，包括了理论知识问答、动作技术、体测成绩（不测长跑）、裁判技术等方面。至于给分，只要能够在课上按老师要求完成任务，成绩就有保障。\n现代物理学（科技类）\n虽然科目名称叫现代物理学，但实际讲述的是非常广泛的物理知识，包括了经典力学、电磁学、振动和波、几何光学、热力学定律、原子物理、相对论等方面的知识。老师是按照大学物理的知识体系进行讲解的，所以会讲一些高中物理没讲过的东西（比如角动量守恒），但是会弱化公式推导。考核由个人报告和小组pre构成，内容均为分析生活中的一个常见的物理现象，选题比较宽泛，很好入手，给分也很棒。\n精益创业（社科类）\n在这门课上，老师会从实践的角度讲解如何规划一个创业方案，并从可持续发展、最小可行性、社会责任等角度来分析创业方案是否合理。至于考核方式，期中：小组用乐高积木来建模出一个创业想法，并为这个创业想法拍摄一部3分钟左右的宣传视频；","title":"来讲一讲我上过的通识/跨学院选修课吧！\n田径（体育类）\n内容包括了长跑、短跑、跨栏、跳高、跳远和铅球这六个项目，老师是裁判员出身，所以课上除了训练动作技术以外，也会讲解田","description":"no description yet","like_count":14,"comment_count":21,"view_count":670,"type":"post","tag":"not tag yet","imageList":"","content_source":null,"comments":[{"id":23281,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":1,"content":"——————END——————\n我讲得比较详细，主要是为了让大家知道这门课是否适合自己，而不是仅仅知道一个结果，给分好不好，严不严之类的。这些东西都不是绝对的，因人而异，我认为选修课对自己胃口很重要，不应该去盲目相信他人的看法。","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23272,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"（接上）期末：个人提交6000字左右的创业策划书。让我个人来评价的话，我并不推荐选这门课，原因嘛，我觉得老师很有想法，但是备课过程中没有验证这些想法的可行性，讲课过于空洞，考核内容严重不合理，会导致完成作业的时候很累。","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23273,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":915,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"\uD83D\uDC4F","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":915,"name":"dgsjfgsiwj","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23274,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"计算机科学专题（跨学院/FIT）\n这是一门讲座课，每个老师上一节课，每门课都会讲一个专题。但是要注意，这些专题都来自于老师们的研究成果，并不局限于计算机的基础知识，所以理解起来比较困难，选读这门课时要慎重。有期末考试，考试为闭卷，全部为选择题，考查课上讲过的所有专题，题目中有少部分为套路固定的计算。","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23277,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"媒介与社会（跨学院/FA）\n讲述媒介的演变极其与社会发展的关系，会从媒介产业、媒介内容、媒介受众这三个方面进行阐述。考核方式一般由pre和论文构成，不同老师间会略有差异，但是这些project的内容都逃不过一个点，那就是需要分析一种媒介的演变过程，并论述这种媒介为何会产生这些变化，和社会发展有何关联","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23279,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":643,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"欢迎回来！！！","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":643,"name":"脾气超级差","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1658825259833.jpg?Expires=1974185254&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=cVqDAV6c37qT%2FyCkpGnFEKtS3TU%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23280,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":1295,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"学长终于发帖子了！这条帖子对我的真的帮助很大！学长辛苦啦","anonymity":1,"any_name":"出前一丁","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":1295,"name":"U_637031633831","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23288,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":1934,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"请问学长我是大一工管的，以后会有几节选修呢？那个科技大师的讲座也是选修吗？我觉得那个还挺有意思的不知道怎么评分","anonymity":1,"any_name":"大潭山车队","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":1934,"name":"Moooohi","avatar_url":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/g2T2gr7SqneMpkZyicqgUxk0ElaP9Toibaic7qRcU9YBQ7ZFdV2ib9Nsz8DmWn3HGrF7z5dPKqUZhXuP0pVvjup4Lw/132"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23291,"parent_id":6240,"type":1,"commentor":781,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"现代物理学感觉很有意思","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":781,"name":"U_300401631199","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23276,"parent_id":23274,"type":2,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"每个学期的专题是不一样的，部分专题内容参考：人工智能、机器学习、密码学基础、网络安全、数字电路基础、区块链、软件工程、时间序列分析......","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=1977811496&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=tLEL737zMefpEHXZzQlS%2Bxz88Ts%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":23278,"parent_id":23277,"type":2,"commentor":682,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我认为在这门课上拿到好成绩，需要一定的人文社科素养，此外不仅要有阅片量，而且最好还要能对你喜欢的媒介产业有着足够深刻的了解，要不然论文会写得很空。别问为什么，问就是我在这门课死得非常惨。","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":682,"name":"~Xenon~","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1662451495431.gif?Expires=197781